me.timothy.tests.database

Class RecentPostMappingTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.timothy.tests.database.RecentPostMappingTest
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    MysqlRecentPostMappingTest

    public class RecentPostMappingTest
extends java.lang.Object
    Describes a test focused on a RecentPostsMapping in a MappingDatabase. The database must be completely empty after each setUp. The database will be modified after each run - do not run against real databases.
    Author:
    Timothy
